{"root":{"data":{"id":"d6a9h152s1k0","created":1734061424820,"text":"理想信念的内涵及重要性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9snx4tk80","created":1734062336411,"text":"什么是理想信念","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-5.999999910592919,"y":-27.999999582767487},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9i4wsf6g0","created":1734061511390,"text":"信念"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9ojq9bcw0","created":1734062013832,"text":"内涵"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9okm8ut40","created":1734062015766,"text":"人们在一定的认识基础上，对某种思想或事物坚信不疑并身体力行的态度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9r6n8lls0","created":1734062220443,"text":"认知，情感和意志的有机统一体"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9ot6otu00","created":1734062034416,"text":"特征"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9ox0mu7c0","created":1734062042757,"text":"执着性：一旦形成，不易改变。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9oxtwzio0","created":1734062044528,"text":"支撑性：信念凝聚着一个国家，一个民族的集体意志，为社会理想的实现提供强\n 大的精神力量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9oyg429s0","created":1734062045870,"text":"多样性：不同人由于社会环境，思想观念，利益需要，人生经历和性格特征等方\n 面的差异，会形成不同的信念"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9i9uqm9c0","created":1734061522150,"text":"理想"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9iu1yuqo0","created":1734061566123,"text":"内涵","layout_right_offset":{"x":21.999999672174567,"y":7.999999880790654}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9j3hjqqw0","created":1734061586656,"text":"理想是人们在实践中形成的、有实现可能性的、对未来社会和自身发展的向往和追求。","layout_right_offset":{"x":623.9999916255475,"y":-18.999999716877937}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9rzrjgn40","created":1734062283830,"text":"人们的世界观，人生观和价值观在奋斗目标上的集中体现","layout_right_offset":{"x":499.9999925494195,"y":-0.9999999850988388}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d6a9j072pog0","created":1734061579492,"text":"特征","layout_right_offset":{"x":-22.999999657273406,"y":42.999999359249955}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d6a9jiy3fog0","created":1734061620308,"text":"超越性：来源现实，超越现实，指向未来。","layout_right_offset":{"x":438.99999345839024,"y":-47.99999928474435},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"